{"id":21346,"date":"2019-09-20T12:57:40","date_gmt":"2019-09-20T05:57:40","guid":{"rendered":"\/?p=21346"},"modified":"2019-12-26T14:56:17","modified_gmt":"2019-12-26T07:56:17","slug":"cach-tao-website-wordpress-ban-hang-va-blogging-sieu-nhe","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"\/wordpress\/cach-tao-website-wordpress-ban-hang-va-blogging-sieu-nhe","title":{"rendered":"C\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o website WordPress b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 blogging \u201csi\u00eau nh\u1eb9\u201d"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"highlight\"><strong>C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o website WordPress b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 blogging si\u00eau nh\u1eb9<\/strong>, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong t\u1ed1i \u01b0u d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m theo h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a ai \u0111\u00f3.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n c\u00e3i, m\u1ed9t website si\u00eau nh\u1eb9 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u0103ng th\u00f4ng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a hosting, t\u0103ng th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng website b\u1ea1n cao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ecdc tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi tr\u00ean blog c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ecdi th\u1ee7 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 plugin v\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea3i trang cho website nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong t\u1ed1i \u01b0u b\u1edfi v\u00ec \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n b\u1ea1n thi\u1ebfu M\u1ed8T COMBO H\u00d2A H\u1ee2P.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh khi b\u1ea1n t\u1eadp h\u1ee3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi nhau nh\u1ea5t. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, m\u1ed9t cache plugin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 si\u00eau t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi theme v\u00e0 plugin kh\u00e1c th\u00ec c\u0169ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 100% s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n: PH\u00c1T HUY 100% S\u1ee8C M\u1ea0NH PH\u1ed0I H\u1ee2P c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 theme v\u00e0 plugin v\u1edbi nhau.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi tr\u00e1nh loay hoay kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft n\u00ean d\u00f9ng g\u00ec cho blog \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea3i trang th\u00ec t\u00f4i s\u1ebd gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u cho b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 combo &#8220;c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n&#8221; m\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u1edfi v\u00ec n\u00f3 TH\u1eacT S\u1ef0 HI\u1ec6U QU\u1ea2.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"tip\"><span class=\"title\">Ch\u00fa \u00dd<\/span>\n<p>B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u1ea1n c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o website b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t WordPress m\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh sau khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e0i WordPress xong. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n, b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y tham kh\u1ea3o b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft&nbsp;<a href=\"\/wordpress\/tao-website-bang-wordpress\/\">c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o website b\u1eb1ng WordPress<\/a> tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>#1. D\u00f9ng WordPress theme si\u00eau nh\u1eb9 &#8211; Suki Theme Pro<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"538\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/suki-theme-1024x538.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-17029\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/suki-theme-1024x538.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/suki-theme-218x114.jpg 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/suki-theme-300x158.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/suki-theme-700x368.jpg 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/suki-theme-768x403.jpg 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/suki-theme.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n cho r\u1eb1ng theme Twenty Nineteen l\u00e0 nh\u1eb9 nh\u1ea5t? B\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng WordPress kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd nhanh b\u1eb1ng static blog?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd suy ngh\u0129 l\u1ea1i b\u1edfi v\u00ec&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"\/out\/sukitheme\" target=\"_blank\">theme Suki<\/a>&nbsp;c\u00f2n nh\u1eb9 h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi theme WordPress m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh Twenty Nineteen v\u00e0 cho t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi static blog.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Mang trong m\u00ecnh nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch duy nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 T\u1ed0C \u0110\u1ed8 nh\u01b0 SVG icon thay v\u00ec d\u00f9ng font awesome hay dashicon, tinh gi\u1ea3n CSS v\u00e0 HTML, ch\u1ec9 d\u00f9ng Vanilla code n\u00ean Suki &#8220;c\u1ef1c nh\u1eb9&#8221; v\u1edbi c\u00e2n n\u1eb7ng 14.9KB v\u00e0 4 HTTPS request. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 theme &#8220;si\u00eau nh\u00e2n&#8221; tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"492\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Suki-theme-sieu-nhe-1024x492.png\" alt=\"Suki Theme Sieu Nhe\" class=\"wp-image-21498\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Suki-theme-sieu-nhe-1024x492.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Suki-theme-sieu-nhe-218x105.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Suki-theme-sieu-nhe-300x144.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Suki-theme-sieu-nhe-700x336.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Suki-theme-sieu-nhe-768x369.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Suki-theme-sieu-nhe.png 1605w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3&nbsp;<a href=\"\/out\/sukipro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Suki Pro<\/a>&nbsp;d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam v\u00e0o h\u01a1n 300 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 t\u0103ng th\u00eam 10KB &#8220;c\u00e2n n\u1eb7ng&#8221;. Tha h\u1ed3 cho b\u1ea1n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 n\u1eb7ng web.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t site \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft blog th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec th\u00edch h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n Suki.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Th\u00eam n\u1eefa b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o website b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed v\u1edbi Suki m\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin ch\u1eafc r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c theme kh\u00e1c s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 Suki.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t theme si\u00eau nh\u1eb9, vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>#2. S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng plugin t\u1ed1i \u01b0u t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd &#8211; Autoptimize<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-plugin-directory\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<div class=\"suki-oembed\"><blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"RfWA4YLmz8\"><a href=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/autoptimize\/\">Autoptimize<\/a><\/blockquote><iframe title=\"&#8220;Autoptimize&#8221; &#8212; Plugin Directory\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/autoptimize\/embed\/#?secret=RfWA4YLmz8\" data-secret=\"RfWA4YLmz8\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"><\/iframe><\/div>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ecdc b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft&nbsp;<a href=\"\/wordpress\/cac-nguyen-tac-giup-tang-toc-website-wordpress\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">6 Nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc V\u00c0NG t\u1ed1i \u01b0u \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c website WordPress th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng<\/a>&nbsp;th\u00ec \u0111\u1eebng hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 n\u00ean t\u1ed1i \u01b0u b\u1eb1ng tay.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch c\u00e1c plugin ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. B\u1ea1n v\u1eabn s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n plugin h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u, \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean m\u00e0 t\u00f4i gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u l\u00e0&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/autoptimize\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">plugin Autoptimize<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u cache plugin cao c\u1ea5p tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed t\u00edch h\u1ee3p c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ednh n\u0103ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 trong m\u1ed9t v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecb cu\u1ed1n h\u00fat v\u00e0o s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Nh\u01b0ng&#8230; s\u1ebd c\u00f3 2 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Qu\u00e1 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p trong c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t sao cho \u0110\u00daNG<\/li><li>T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 trong m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1t<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Theo kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i th\u00ec plugin cache ch\u1ec9 n\u00ean ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t plugin si\u00eau nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 Autoptimize l\u00e0m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 N\u00c9N FILE.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed9t \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 Autoptimize m\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t y\u00eau th\u00edch \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh c\u1ef1c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 hi\u1ebfm khi x\u1ea3y ra l\u1ed7i xung \u0111\u1ed9t.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00e1ch b\u1ea1n c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh Autoptimize nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>T\u1ed1i \u01b0u HTML, Javascript v\u00e0 CSS ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi &#8220;Ba l\u1ea7n b\u1ea5m ch\u1ecdn&#8221; &#8211; Xong<\/li><li>\u0110\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u &#8220;Optimize images on the fly and serve them from Shortpixel&#8217;s global CDN&#8221; (n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3&nbsp;<a href=\"\/shortpixel-service\/\">Shortpixel tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed<\/a>, c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ed1ng).<\/li><li>Font preconnect, 3rd party Preconnect, Remove Emoji, Remove query String v\u00e0 t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh Async JavaScript (T\u1ea3i b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 Javascript b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i).<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Huong-dan-cai-dat-Autoptimize-buoc-1.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"532\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Huong-dan-cai-dat-Autoptimize-buoc-1-1024x532.png\" alt=\"Huong Dan Cai Dat Autoptimize Buoc 1\" class=\"wp-image-21490\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Huong-dan-cai-dat-Autoptimize-buoc-1-1024x532.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Huong-dan-cai-dat-Autoptimize-buoc-1-218x113.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Huong-dan-cai-dat-Autoptimize-buoc-1-300x156.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Huong-dan-cai-dat-Autoptimize-buoc-1-700x364.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Huong-dan-cai-dat-Autoptimize-buoc-1-768x399.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Huong-dan-cai-dat-Autoptimize-buoc-1.png 1689w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>\u0110\u00e1nh 3 d\u1ea5u &#8220;stick&#8221; l\u00e0 xong<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-autoptimize-buoc-3.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"542\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-autoptimize-buoc-3-1024x542.png\" alt=\"Cai Dat Autoptimize Buoc 3\" class=\"wp-image-21491\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-autoptimize-buoc-3-1024x542.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-autoptimize-buoc-3-218x115.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-autoptimize-buoc-3-300x159.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-autoptimize-buoc-3-700x370.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-autoptimize-buoc-3-768x406.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-autoptimize-buoc-3.png 1676w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1ed1i \u01b0u nhanh c\u0169ng v\u1edbi 3 stick<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Ph\u1ea7n c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t Image trong Autoptimize, b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y xem \u1edf m\u1ee5c k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"tip\"><span class=\"title\">Ch\u00fa \u00dd<\/span>\n<p>\u1ede tab Preconnect, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o async JavaScript v\u00ec n\u00f3 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Javascript Render Block \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n n\u1ebfu external Javascript b\u1ea1n nh\u00fang v\u00e0o website kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 async hay defer loading.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>#3. T\u1ed1i \u01b0u to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u1ea3nh &#8211; Shortpixel<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-plugin-directory\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<div class=\"suki-oembed\"><blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"3xOmLzpzDj\"><a href=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/shortpixel-image-optimiser\/\">ShortPixel Image Optimizer<\/a><\/blockquote><iframe title=\"&#8220;ShortPixel Image Optimizer&#8221; &#8212; Plugin Directory\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/shortpixel-image-optimiser\/embed\/#?secret=3xOmLzpzDj\" data-secret=\"3xOmLzpzDj\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"><\/iframe><\/div>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"\/out\/shortpixel\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Shortpixel (opens in a new tab)\">Shortpixel<\/a> l\u00e0 top plugin n\u00e9n \u1ea3nh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t hi\u1ebfm x\u1ea3y ra l\u1ed7i khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng Shortpixel r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p l\u1ed7i, plugin ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0 nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1n k\u00e9m t\u00e0i nguy\u00ean c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hai trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng m\u00e0 t\u00f4i khuy\u00ean b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a Shortpixel \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb \u1ea3nh d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng WebP<\/li><li>T\u1ea3i \u1ea3nh d\u00f9ng CDN (b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n Shortpixle credit) &#8211; L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u00eam<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>D\u00f9 WebP ch\u1ec9 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf tr\u00ean h\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1i Google l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh nh\u01b0 tr\u00ecnh duy\u1ec7t Chrome, tr\u00ecnh duy\u1ec7t di \u0111\u1ed9ng Android v\u00e0 \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng Chrome di \u0111\u1ed9ng, nh\u01b0ng nhi\u00eau \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m cho b\u1ea1n c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u0103ng th\u00f4ng hosting t\u1eeb 50% \u0111\u1ebfn 70% t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap website b\u1ea1n nhanh h\u01a1n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. C\u1ef1c l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 blog, c\u00e1c website th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed (d\u00f9ng Woocomerce) s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea3nh hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb tr\u00ean m\u1ed7i trang v\u00e0 n\u00f3 s\u1ebd mau ch\u00f3ng h\u00fat c\u1ea1n b\u0103ng th\u00f4ng hosting c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi l\u00e0m ch\u1eadm website b\u1ea1n &#8220;r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u&#8221;.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nhanh v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u00e1ch b\u1eadt t\u00ednh n\u0103ng WebP trong Shortpixel.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, Shortpixel s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u1ea3nh tr\u00ean website b\u1ea1n th\u00e0nh <code>&lt;picture&gt;<\/code> tag, v\u1edbi <code>&lt;picture&gt;<\/code> tag th\u00ec n\u00f3 s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u1ecdn ngu\u1ed3n \u1ea3nh ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb \u1ea3nh.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u00f3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa n\u00f3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc thumbnail ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. R\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i, l\u00e0 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng 2 trong 1 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 website b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-Shortpixel.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"525\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-Shortpixel-1024x525.png\" alt=\"Cai Dat Shortpixel\" class=\"wp-image-21489\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-Shortpixel-1024x525.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-Shortpixel-218x112.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-Shortpixel-300x154.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-Shortpixel-700x359.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-Shortpixel-768x393.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-Shortpixel.png 1739w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>B\u1eadt t\u00ednh n\u0103ng WebP trong Shortpixel v\u1edbi &lt;Picture&gt; tag <br>(l\u1ea7n t\u1ea3i trang \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 d\u00f9ng WebP lu\u00f4n, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i qua cache)<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 t\u0103ng nhanh h\u01a1n n\u1eefa t\u00f4i khuy\u00ean b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Shortpixel CDN, n\u00f3 s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng resize \u1ea3nh tr\u00ean Shortpixel hosting v\u00e0 cache nh\u1eefng \u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3 qua CDN cache, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u00edch h\u1ee3p v\u00e0o site b\u1ea1n v\u1edbi k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ea3nh ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cao nh\u1ea5t (trong khi<code> &lt;picture&gt;<\/code> tag \u1edf tr\u00ean ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn file \u1ea3nh ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o media setting thmbnail m\u00e0 th\u00f4i).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-autoptimize-buoc-2.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"510\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-autoptimize-buoc-2-1024x510.png\" alt=\"Cai Dat Autoptimize Buoc 2\" class=\"wp-image-21488\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-autoptimize-buoc-2-1024x510.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-autoptimize-buoc-2-218x108.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-autoptimize-buoc-2-300x149.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-autoptimize-buoc-2-700x348.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-autoptimize-buoc-2-768x382.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-autoptimize-buoc-2.png 1690w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>B\u1eadt Shortpixel CDN r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n b\u1eb1ng Autoptimize<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>L\u1ee3i \u00edch l\u00e0 khi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p s\u1ebd m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa gi\u1ea3m t\u1ea3i b\u0103ng th\u00f4ng cho hosting v\u00e0 gi\u00fap website nhanh h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh Shortpixel? H\u00e3y tham kh\u1ea3o nhanh&nbsp;<a href=\"\/docs\/shortpixel\">c\u00e1ch c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh Shortpixel<\/a>&nbsp;m\u00e0 t\u00f4i d\u00f9ng h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng CuongThach.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"tip\"><span class=\"title\">Ch\u00fa \u00dd<\/span>\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng <b>Shortpixel CDN<\/b> b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t \u1ea3nh l\u00e0 <b>Glossy<\/b> trong khi n\u00e9n \u1ea3nh m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh Shortpixel l\u00e0 Lossy. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e9o tr\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb r\u00f5 n\u00e9t. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Shortpixel.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>#4. C\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t cache plugin l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi Autoptimize &#8211; Cache Enabler<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-plugin-directory\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<div class=\"suki-oembed\"><blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"IeSdTgqC4h\"><a href=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/cache-enabler\/\">Cache Enabler &#8211; WordPress Cache<\/a><\/blockquote><iframe title=\"&#8220;Cache Enabler &#8211; WordPress Cache&#8221; &#8212; Plugin Directory\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/cache-enabler\/embed\/#?secret=IeSdTgqC4h\" data-secret=\"IeSdTgqC4h\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"><\/iframe><\/div>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/cache-enabler\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Cache Enabler<\/a>&nbsp;l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cache plugin si\u00eau nh\u1eb9 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 100% v\u1edbi Autoptimize v\u00e0 Shortpixel.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Shortpixel gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb \u1ea3nh WebP ngay t\u1eeb l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng gh\u00e9 website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n th\u00ec Cache Enabler s\u1ebd gi\u00fap cache WebP ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"hint\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p, b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 d\u00f9ng Shortpixel CDN th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n t\u00ednh n\u0103ng cache WebP n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Khi b\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng chung v\u1edbi Autoptimize b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n disbale t\u00ednh n\u0103ng minify c\u1ee7a Cache Enabler l\u00e0 XONG. H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 vi\u1ec7c minify l\u1ea1i cho Autoptimize. C\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t kh6ong th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-cache-enabler.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"597\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-cache-enabler-1024x597.png\" alt=\"Cai Dat Cache Enabler\" class=\"wp-image-21487\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-cache-enabler-1024x597.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-cache-enabler-218x127.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-cache-enabler-300x175.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-cache-enabler-700x408.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-cache-enabler-768x448.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cai-dat-cache-enabler.png 1486w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Disable t\u00ednh n\u0103ng Minification v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u ch\u1ecdn cho cache WebP<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"tip\"><span class=\"title\">Ch\u00fa \u00dd<\/span>\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/plugins\/litespeed-cache\/\" target=\"_blank\">Litespeed cache plugin<\/a>&nbsp;c\u0169ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 Cache Enabler b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng thay th\u1ebf n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ch\u1ea1y tr\u00ean server OpenLiteSpeed.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>#5. C\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng CDN \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o website WordPress nhanh h\u01a1n khi hosting server c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u1edf&#8230; M\u1ef9 &#8211; Cloudflare (L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn)<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"489\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cloudflare-CDN-network-1024x489.png\" alt=\"Cloudflare Cdn Network\" class=\"wp-image-21483\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cloudflare-CDN-network-1024x489.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cloudflare-CDN-network-218x104.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cloudflare-CDN-network-300x143.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cloudflare-CDN-network-700x335.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cloudflare-CDN-network-768x367.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/Cloudflare-CDN-network.png 1881w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Khi hosting b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 hay Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u th\u00ec b\u1ea1n b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c n\u00ean c\u00f3 CDN n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n website b\u1ecb ch\u1eadm.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cloudflare CDN mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhanh, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c plugin tr\u00ean s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t combo ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Automation s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Cloudflare CDN m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi b\u1ea1n thao t\u00e1c th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cache Enabler sau khi cache s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean Cloudflare v\u00e0 cache l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Shortpixel v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng xung \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi Cloudflare n\u1ebfu d\u00f9ng Shortpixel CDN. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng Shortpixel CDN th\u00ec Cloudflare CDN v\u1eabn s\u1ebd h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cache WebP, n\u00ean b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n lo l\u1eafng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"tip\"><span class=\"title\">Ch\u00fa \u00dd<\/span>\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng Woocomerce \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o website b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng th\u00ec b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 cache c\u1ee7a Cloudflare tr\u1eeb khi d\u00f9ng Cloudflare Pro tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed, gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 d\u00f9ng nh\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p CDN tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed kh\u00e1c gi\u00e1 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Cloudflare Pro. V\u1edbi blogger th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o blog v\u1edbi Cloudflare kh\u00e1 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>L\u1eddi k\u1ebft&#8230;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi, c\u00e1ch ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p combo n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o website WordPress si\u00eau nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd mu\u1ed1n v\u00e0 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m h\u00e0ng gi\u1edd t\u1ed1i \u01b0u.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 quen d\u00f9ng c\u00e1c plugin cao c\u1ea5p tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, h\u00e3y th\u1eed chuy\u1ec3n qua b\u1ed9 combo n\u00e0y v\u00e0 so s\u00e1nh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a combo.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u00f4i c\u0169ng tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng combo t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng th\u1eddi gian th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m s\u1ebd ti\u00eau t\u1ed1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, n\u00ean d\u00f9ng n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c ch\u00ednh h\u01a1n th\u00ec t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>N\u1ebfu c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 trong c\u00e1ch h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn t\u1ea1o website WordPress nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u1edbi combo tr\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i ho\u1eb7c c\u00f2n c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn nh\u00e9.<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o website Wordpress b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 blogging si\u00eau nh\u1eb9, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong t\u1ed1i \u01b0u. T\u1ea1i sao?<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":17,"featured_media":21470,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"close","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[42],"tags":[3,46,16],"featured_image_urls":{"full":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/cach-tao-website-wordpress-ban-hang-va-blogging-sieu-nhe.png",1024,512,false],"thumbnail":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/cach-tao-website-wordpress-ban-hang-va-blogging-sieu-nhe-300x150.png",270,135,true],"medium":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/cach-tao-website-wordpress-ban-hang-va-blogging-sieu-nhe-700x350.png",700,350,true],"medium_large":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/cach-tao-website-wordpress-ban-hang-va-blogging-sieu-nhe-768x384.png",768,384,true],"large":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/cach-tao-website-wordpress-ban-hang-va-blogging-sieu-nhe-1024x51